<a href="https://pluralistic.net/2022/10/21/let-me-summarize/"><img decoding="async" class="xmasthead_link jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i0.wp.com/craphound.com/images/21Oct2022.jpg?w=840&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/craphound.com/images/21Oct2022.jpg?w=840&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img data-lazy-fallback="1" decoding="async" class="xmasthead_link" src="https://i0.wp.com/craphound.com/images/21Oct2022.jpg?w=840&#038;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" /></noscript></a></p>
