<p>#15yrsago Italy proposes a Ministry of Blogging with mandatory blog-licensing <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20071021025947/https://beppegrillo.it/eng/2007/10/the_leviprodi_law_and_the_end.html">https://web.archive.org/web/20071021025947/https://beppegrillo.it/eng/2007/10/the_leviprodi_law_and_the_end.html</a></p>
<p>#15yrsago German music publisher claims that nothing is public domain until its copyright runs out in every country <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20071022112555/https://www.michaelgeist.ca/content/view/2308/125/">https://web.archive.org/web/20071022112555/https://www.michaelgeist.ca/content/view/2308/125/</a></p>
